The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Petr Cech improving

London: Chelsea goalkeeper Petr Cech is fully conscious and his condition is improving following surgery on his fractured skull, the club said in a statement on Monday. 

He is now fully conscious following the operation and the effects of the anaesthetic. He is talking with his wife Martina as well as the Chelsea and hospital medical teams who have now given permission for visitors, the club said. 

Several members of the Chelsea management and team including Jose Mourinho and John Terry visited him this afternoon, while Carlo Cudicini was at the training ground today. (Reuters) 




